channel.title: [PI] Need help with SQL Hiscores [PI]
channel.description: Hey - I have a problem, i have created the hiscores for my RSPS and i would like people to visit it but they cannot because my no-ip doesnt work in the browser, any suggestions or anything, thanks.

item.title: [PI] Need help with SQL Hiscores [PI]
item.dc:creator: @Marine5287 Marine5287
item.description:
@Marine5287 wrote:

If I’m thinking what you’re thinking about your no-ip in the browser, then try putting in your default gateway.(Ex: 192.168.1.1) You can find the default gateway by going into your cmd prompt and typing ipconfig Just go until you see the first “Default Gateway”. Then search it in your adress bar.
